{"tid":382414,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[開學啦] 明天終於要開學","createTime":"2017-08-31T16:23:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-01T12:26:11.000Z","uid":28918,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2957418e392e0174275318432cacb3e4c41439fd","tid":382414,"uid":28918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T16:23:44.000Z","msg":"終於可以少左班中學小學雞係度<br />\n<br />\n連登本身都已經低質左好多<br />\n你老味暑假多左咁撚多低質會員<br />\n<br />\n佢地又唔撚係5p黎bo<br />\n但就係好撚多真心膠<br />\n<br />\n多左好多人特登開post搏屌<br />\n都算，一望入面D留言，個個爭住屌<br />\n<br />\n都算，入面D爭論真係小學雞都不如<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一個搏屌既post都可以比樓主屌返轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋多左好多人生攻擊留言<br />\n入面總有好多：又唔見你老母比我屌<br />\n之類，成陣柒味<br />\n我諗佢地應該覺得咁樣講好型，串到人地全家，搞到人地還擊唔到<br />\n<br />\n點都好啦，明天準備返學啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a05a043f3a299c3d8c239ec87bdd10b1c336f197","tid":382414,"uid":79502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T16:35:41.000Z","msg":"4-9先開"},{"pid":"16eaa8bc5ec2b3a73570e8c0d6c13ac613bac3f1","tid":382414,"uid":28918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T00:14:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>4-9先開</blockquote><br />\n做咩姐你"},{"pid":"7388a92ed6736bcbefd0037b5ae5aaa385e30811","tid":382414,"uid":128150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T00:19:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>4-9先開</blockquote><br />\n做咩姐你</blockquote><br />\n你咁屌發佢地重開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b9bb498249f3f0fd6c67a0b49956d5f7f27b227","tid":382414,"uid":23400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T01:31:40.000Z","msg":"連登不嬲係咁，唔係暑假先發生咁多野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"